成！终于完成了今年的体检kpi，实在是太不容易了，每年体检就像是去考试一样，猫猫的体检报告就是我的成绩单，还好今年的“成绩”还不错，比去年还有点提升，实在是可喜可贺可喜可贺！", "copyright": "1", "title": "医生：指标异常！必须少吃肉！橘猫听完急了", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1664616622, "length": "04:25", "video_review": 804, "aid": 603611506, "bvid": "BV1XB4y177Ri", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16512, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 470, "typeid": 218, "play": 489315, "pic": "http://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/5f72c16cc3e73572ad2b9618a8bd218b143cf241.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "在成都被隔离了十多天，每天就只能在家里待着，想给猫猫做点新装扮但是又买不到，幸好我灵机一动，家里的各种食材还是很多的嘛！（本视频拍摄过程中没有任何食材被浪费~）", "copyright": "1", "title": "当铲屎官被隔离在家，会对猫做多么丧尽天良的事", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "created": 1663409101, "length": "03:51", "video_review": 1634, "aid": 858173723, "bvid": "BV1SV4y1M7Bm", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 0, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16512, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 1220, "typeid": 218, "play": 1465653, "pic": "http://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/25f2ad0cbaae0231dd97e3f0bf626c2153de3a65.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "其实，小猫咪的性格是会随着时间的推移发生改变的，即便是已经成年的猫猫，也会给铲屎官带来不一样的惊喜（xia）体验！但是无论如何，都要继续宠爱它们呀！谁让它们是毛茸茸的小猫咪呢～", "copyright": "1", "title": "没想到，我被一只猫骗了整整五年！？", "review": 0, "author": "花花与三猫CatLive", "mid": 9008159, "c